ROI of Security Culture Programs
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Calculate Return on Investment (ROI) for cybersecurity culture programs using quantitative metrics
Develop Python-based models to analyze cost-benefit relationships in security initiatives
Create data visualizations to communicate ROI findings to stakeholders
Generate professional reports demonstrating the business value of security culture investments
Apply financial analysis techniques to cybersecurity program evaluation
Prerequisites
Before starting this lab, students should have:

Basic Python programming knowledge (functions, data structures, file I/O)
Understanding of fundamental cybersecurity concepts
Familiarity with basic financial metrics (costs, benefits, ROI calculations)
